logo: Icetea Software

  ‚Ä¢ All elements are centered on a white background.

Text & Typography :
  ‚Ä¢ "Icetea" uses a light, sans-serif font.
  ‚Ä¢ "Software" uses a bold, sans-serif font for emphasis.

Dimensions & Placement :
  ‚Ä¢ The geometric symbol is placed above the company name, occupying roughly the top half of the logo.
  ‚Ä¢ The text is horizontally aligned and centered beneath the symbol.

Analysis :
  ‚Ä¢ The logo uses red to convey energy and attention, while the bold "Software" highlights the company's core business.
